Markdown
========
Markdown is a text format documentation language  which can be used to easily document software and systems
developed with the key design goal of readability. Modern editors like Atom, VScode etc and web based versioning systems like GitLab and GitHub support markdown. **Typora** is an excellent markdown editor with automatic preview.


